# Hardened sshd_config managed in dotfiles (do not restart sshd automatically)
# Based on best practices for public-key only, disabling root login, and minimal attack surface.

Port 22
Protocol 2

PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes

LoginGraceTime 30s
MaxAuthTries 3
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2

AllowTcpForwarding no
X11Forwarding no
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server
